description: Create your own Professional Solutions. Flexygo allows you to immediatly build incredible Solutions for companies, professionals and individuals. For easy installation visit https://nuget.flexygo.com/
releaseNotes:
New features:  
 Loading effect when dependency is executed
 New passbook integration
 Add new file import functionality to the system
 Add holidays view to tracking scheduler settings.
 Add has-tools, has-notify, has-primary, ha-outstanding classes for changing input color.
 Add Google sample code to create, update and delete contacts and events and fix google contacts sync
 Add CCO to mails and notice sentences and fix line break
 Added Blind Carbon Copy (BCC or CCO) in Notice Sentences 

Fixes: 
 Avoid parsing sql statements in object views when updating or inserting
 Clean rotation metadata on device images before uploading to flexygo platform
 Redirect to login page when LDAP login failed
 Fix problem in guest access in user must change password checking.
 Fixed editgrid on saving and editing an image type field
 Node Faculties
 We increase the size of the url field of the navigation nodes for large urls
 Password requirements are now correctly gotten on user created with manual password
 Send ERP Documents
 Fix Test Entity and Collection when dataview has context vars for parsing.
title: Flexygo
